00:44:21,980 --> 00:44:25,510
♫ And live in the blissful here and now ♫

526
00:44:25,510 --> 00:44:30,970
♫ I will protect only you from now on, by all means ♫

527
00:44:30,970 --> 00:44:37,190
♫ I vow, in sickness and in health ♫

528
00:44:37,190 --> 00:44:40,250
♫ I'll dedicate my love to you ♫

529
00:44:40,250 --> 00:44:46,110
She had no idea an uncontrollable storm...

530
00:44:46,110 --> 00:44:48,340
was already at her doorstep.

531
00:44:48,340 --> 00:44:50,620
I'm home.

532
00:44:52,830 --> 00:44:54,620
You're late.

533
00:44:55,390 --> 00:44:59,830
Oh, Negi!

534
00:44:59,830 --> 00:45:01,300
Hey.

535
00:45:01,300 --> 00:45:03,120
What about me?

536
00:45:05,030 --> 00:45:11,910
♫ You see? Here we go again; we are invulnerable ♫

537
00:45:11,910 --> 00:45:15,550
♫ Impregnable, even when facing an enemy ♫

538
00:45:15,550 --> 00:45:18,520
♫ We'll challenge them head-on ♫

539
00:45:18,520 --> 00:45:21,160
- Oh?
- What?

540
00:45:21,160 --> 00:45:23,580
Nothing.

541
00:45:24,880 --> 00:45:28,460
♫ If I'm with you, it will never ever end ♫

542
00:45:28,460 --> 00:45:31,320
- What?
- Yeah?

543
00:45:31,320 --> 00:45:33,620
Expecting something else?

544
00:45:33,620 --> 00:45:36,770
Excuse me? No.

545
00:45:42,080 --> 00:45:43,760
Welcome home.

546
00:45:52,930 --> 00:45:56,790
She could only assume their love was eternal.

547
00:45:57,900 --> 00:45:59,970
[Preview]
I think I'm happier than I've ever been.

548
00:45:59,970 --> 00:46:01,380
Thanks for marrying me.

549
00:46:01,380 --> 00:46:02,680
We are very sorry.

550
00:46:02,680 --> 00:46:04,230
No matter what you might do, we won't give in.

551
00:46:04,230 --> 00:46:05,660
Are you sure about that?

552
00:46:05,660 --> 00:46:08,280
Weren't you supposed to make my sister happy?

553
00:46:08,280 --> 00:46:10,990
- I'm just tired of everything.
- You said you wanted us to be family.

554
00:46:10,990 --> 00:46:13,110
You're irritating me!
